Former Big Brother Housemate, “Pepper dem” edition, Diane Russet has revealed that she would love to see Lesbianism legalized in Nigeria. Diane made this known in a post shared via her insta story on Tuesday. The former reality Tv star, asked her followers to share their secret that no one knew nothing about. Following the development, a follower had replied saying “ I am so attracted to girls. I wish lesbianism was legal, I would love to date a girl.” In a response, Diane expressed doubts that the idea will be welcomed in Nigeria but also revealed that she would love to see it legalized too. “This conversation though, I doubt Nigeria will because we are too religious. “Won’t type much before someone misquotes me. “I would love to see it legalized though” she said. See picture below… <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-853103" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_5806.jpg" alt="" width="1242" height="2025" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_5806.jpg 1242w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_5806-184x300.jpg 184w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_5806-628x1024.jpg 628w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_5806-942x1536.jpg 942w" sizes="(max-width: 1242px) 100vw, 1242px">